<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Device Login Detected</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        .info {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">New Device Login Detected <i class="fas fa-user-lock"></i></h1>
        <p>We have detected a new login from a device. Here are the details:</p>
        <div class="info">
            <strong><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Browser:</strong> <%= browserDetails.browser %><br>
            <strong><i class="fas fa-laptop"></i> Operating System:</strong> <%= os %><br>
            <strong><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Browser Version:</strong> <%= browserDetails.version %><br>
            <strong><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Date & Time:</strong> <%= new Date(dateTimeAt).toLocaleString() %><br>
            <strong><i class="fas fa-address-card"></i> IP Address:</strong> <%= ip %><br>
        </div>
        <p>If this was not you, please secure your account.</p>
        <div class="footer text-center">
            <p>Thank you,<br>Your Security Team <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
